                        There a load of new free Bootstrap 3 ready templates at Bootply. All of these templates are free and don't require extensive customization to the Bootstrap baseline.
                        %hr
                          %ul.list-unstyled
                            %li
                              %a{:href => "http://www.bootply.com/templates"} Dashboard
                            %li
                              %a{:href => "http://www.bootply.com/templates"} Darkside
                            %li
                              %a{:href => "http://www.bootply.com/templates"} Greenfield
