                    .panel-heading
                      %h4 What Is Bootstrap?
                    .panel-body
                      Bootstrap is front end frameworkto build custom web applications that are fast, responsive &amp; intuitive. It consist of CSS and HTML for typography, forms, buttons, tables, grids, and navigation along with custom-built jQuery plug-ins and support for responsive layouts. With dozens of reusable components for navigation, pagination, labels, alerts etc..
                / main col right
                .col-sm-7
                  .well
                    %form.form
                      %h4 Sign-up
                      .input-group.text-center
                        %input.form-control.input-lg{:placeholder => "Enter your email address", :type => "text"}
                          %span.input-group-btn
                            %button.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary{:type => "button"} OK
                  .panel.panel-default
                    .panel-heading
                      %a.pull-right{:href => "#"} View all
                      %h4 Bootply Editor &amp; Code Library
                    .panel-body
                      %p
                        %img.img-circle.pull-right{:src => "//placehold.it/150x150"}
                          %a{:href => "#"} The Bootstrap Playground
                      .clearfix
                      %hr
                        Design, build, test, and prototype using Bootstrap in real-time from your Web browser. Bootply combines the power of hand-coded HTML, CSS and JavaScript with the benefits of responsive design using Bootstrap. Find and showcase Bootstrap-ready snippets in the 100% free Bootply.com code repository.
                  .panel.panel-default
                    .panel-heading
                      %a.pull-right{:href => "#"} View all
                      %h4 Stackoverflow
                    .panel-body
                      %img.img-circle.pull-right{:src => "//placehold.it/150x150"}
                        %a{:href => "#"} Keyword: Bootstrap
                        .clearfix
                        %hr
                          %p
                            If you're looking for help with Bootstrap code, the
                            %code twitter-bootstrap
                            tag at
                            %a{:href => "http://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/twitter-bootstrap"} Stackoverflow
                            is a good place to find answers.
                          %hr
                            %form
                              .input-group
                                .input-group-btn
                                  %button.btn.btn-default +1
                                  %button.btn.btn-default
                                    %i.glyphicon.glyphicon-share
                                %input.form-control{:placeholder => "Add a comment..", :type => "text"}
                  .panel.panel-default
                    .panel-heading
                      %a.pull-right{:href => "#"} View all
                      %h4 Portlet Heading
                    .panel-body
                      %ul.list-group
                        %li.list-group-item Modals
                        %li.list-group-item Sliders / Carousel
                        %li.list-group-item Thumbnails
                  .panel.panel-default
                    .panel-thumbnail
                      %img.img-responsive{:src => "/assets/example/bg_4.jpg"}/
                    .panel-body
                      %p.lead Social Good
                      %p 1,200 Followers, 83 Posts
                      %p
                        %img{:height => "28px", :src => "https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-5cTTMHjjnzs/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAFk/vgza68M4p2s/s28-c-k-no/photo.jpg", :width => "28px"}
                          %img{:height => "28px", :src => "https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-6aFMDiaLg5M/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAABdM/XjnG8z60Ug0/s28-c-k-no/photo.jpg", :width => "28px"}
                            %img{:height => "28px", :src => "https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-9Yw2jNffJlE/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAAA/u3WcFXvK-g8/s28-c-k-no/photo.jpg", :width => "28px"}
              / /row
              .row
                .col-sm-6
                  %a{:href => "#"} Twitter
                  %small.text-muted |
                  %a{:href => "#"} Facebook
                  %small.text-muted |
                  %a{:href => "#"} Google+
              #footer.row
                .col-sm-6
                .col-sm-6
                  %p
                    %a.pull-right{:href => "#"} ©Copyright 2013
              %hr
                %h4.text-center
                  %a{:href => "http://bootply.com/96266", :target => "ext"} Download this Template @Bootply
                %hr
            / /col-9
          / /padding
        / /main
